fixed.c
-------
	enum fixed_type {ICON, RECT, TEXT, SEARCH};
	@type-action-x-y-w-h-r-halign-valign-fgcol-bgcol-content
		NOTES:
		  - x, y: distance from edge
		  - 'content' is icon_path or text
		  - For RECT, a 1px thick border will be drawn using fgcol
